content.rendered: “My Personal Horoscope” focuses especially on the traits and truths of your Rising sign- the sign which was ascending on the Earth’s eastern horizon at the time when you were born and which suggests the sign which you were meant to be. To fully understand your unique birth chart it is essential to have knowledge of both your Sun sign (Zodiac sign) and your Rising sign. Regarding your Sun sign and Rising sign together provides you with vital information about how you differ compared to others of the same Sun sign.
